\par\par \uc2 T Magazine; Fashion & Beauty\par {\*\bkmkstart toc4}{\*\bkmkend toc4}\b \uc2 9 Models to Watch This Season\b0\par\par\uc2 By HILARY MOSS \par \uc2 1,036 \uc2 words\par \uc2 8 February 2017\par 15:44\par \uc2 NYTimes.com Feed\par \uc2 NYTFEED\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2017. The New York Times Company. All Rights Reserved. \par \par \uc2 Ahead of the fall/winter 2017 shows, T and the casting director Arianna Pradarelli round up the runway\u8217\'20\'19s most intriguing fresh faces \u8212\'20\'14 some making their {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/subjects/n/new_york_fashion_week/index.html?inline=nyt-classifier"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 New York Fashion Week}}}\uc2  debuts, others a few seasons in.\par \par \uc2 Wallette Watson\par \par \uc2 21, N.C.\par \par \uc2 Originally from Raleigh, the now New York-based Watson walked at Yeezy and Coach 1941 last season and in Paris for labels like Saint Laurent, \uc2 Christian Dior\uc2 , Valentino and \uc2 Sonia Rykiel\uc2 . For fall/winter 2017, expect to see her in London and Milan as well. (Her favorite way to pass the time backstage, she notes, is with a deck of cards.) \u8220\'20\'1CIf I weren\u8217\'20\'19t modeling, I would be singing \u8212\'20\'14 working on an album, and in the studio day and night,\u8221\'20\'1D she says. \u8220\'20\'1CI think I started singing when I came out of the womb!\u8221\'20\'1D Her talents also include dancing \u8212\'20\'14 she was classically trained in ballet. \u8220\'20\'1CBeing your own amazingly beautiful self is what sets you apart from everyone else,\u8221\'20\'1D Watson adds, \u8220\'20\'1Cno matter what anyone says.\u8221\'20\'1D\par \par \uc2 Represented by {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.qmodels.com/"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2  Q Model Management }}}\uc2  .\par \par \uc2 _____\par \par \uc2 L\u233\'00\'E9a Julian\par \par \uc2 18, France\par \par \uc2 Julian recently traded her hometown Toulouse for Paris to further pursue modeling; she has frequented the European runways since age 16, after making her debut at Valentino\u8217\'20\'19s fall 2015 haute couture spectacular in Rome. But this will be the first season that she adds New York to her docket. \u8220\'20\'1CTraveling is the best part of the job,\u8221\'20\'1D she says. \u8220\'20\'1CIf I weren\u8217\'20\'19t modeling, I think I would be at \b \highlight22\uc2 university\b0 \highlight\uc2  working on linguistics and communications \u8212\'20\'14 actually, thanks to modeling, I\u8217\'20\'19m learning a lot, because I\u8217\'20\'19ve met so many people from all over the world already.\u8221\'20\'1D Julian also made sure to mention her hidden talent: the ability to quickly solve a Rubik\u8217\'20\'19s Cube.\par \par \uc2 Represented by {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.thesocietymanagement.com/landing.aspx"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2  The Society Management }}}\uc2  .\par \par \uc2 _____\par \par \uc2 Manuela Sanchez\par \par \uc2 16, Dominican Republic\par \par \uc2 Sanchez started her runway career as a Saint Laurent exclusive for spring/summer 2017 and walked in {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.nytimes.com/slideshow/2017/01/24/t-magazine/fashion/iris-van-herpen-giambattista-valli-paris-couture-fashion-week-shows/s/24tmag-iris-dior-valli-slide-F2C2.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 Giambattista Valli\u8217\'20\'19s couture show}}}\uc2  last month. She will be making the rounds at the European shows and says she also loves to dance \u8212\'20\'14 and eat Nutella.\par \par \uc2 Represented by {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.viva-paris.com/"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2  Viva Model Management London }}}\uc2  .\par \par \uc2 _____\par \par \uc2 Shujing Zhou\par \par \uc2 21, China\par \par \uc2 A self-described chameleon (\u8220\'20\'1CI am always changing my style,\u8221\'20\'1D she says), Zhou walked in a handful of spring/summer 2017 shows \u8212\'20\'14 \uc2 Pringle of Scotland\uc2  and Max Mara among them \u8212\'20\'14 with shaggy, shoulder-length orange hair. She debuted her current cropped haircut at Balenciaga and kept it for the fashion house\u8217\'20\'19s ad campaign, and will likely transform again during what will be her first New York show season. Zhou doesn\u8217\'20\'19t shy away from dramatic gigs, either. \u8220\'20\'1CI once had to do a shoot underwater, which was very challenging, as I cannot swim,\u8221\'20\'1D she says. \u8220\'20\'1CI did it, though, and in the end, the pictures were beautiful.\u8221\'20\'1D\par \par \uc2 Represented by {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.nextmanagement.com/"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2  Next Model Management }}}\uc2  .\par \par \uc2 _____\par \par \uc2 Amber Buuren\par \par \uc2 16, the Netherlands\par \par \uc2 The part-time model (and part-time high school student) from Apeldoorn will debut on the runway at the upcoming shows, and plans to keep her family in the loop by chatting with them backstage. She hopes to one day study medicine and become a pediatrician. For now, \u8220\'20\'1CI feel very connected to our earth and its animal life,\u8221\'20\'1D she says. \u8220\'20\'1CClimate change and the extinction of so many species are examples of things that make me worry. I know one person can\u8217\'20\'19t save the world, but I do the best I can, by not eating meat, for example.\u8221\'20\'1D\par \par \uc2 Represented by {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.womenmanagement.com/"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2  Women Management Paris }}}\uc2  .\par \par \uc2 _____\par \par \uc2 Bl\u233\'00\'E9snya Minher\par \par \uc2 19, Angola\par \par \uc2 A native of the Lunda Norte province, Minher has already made a mark in Paris \u8212\'20\'14 specifically on the spring/summer 2017 runways of \uc2 Christian Dior\uc2 , Valentino, Miu Miu and Kenzo. She also walked in Valentino\u8217\'20\'19s haute couture show last month and posed for the fashion house\u8217\'20\'19s latest ad campaign. Now, she\u8217\'20\'19s in New York for her first full show season (and her inaugural trip Stateside). \u8220\'20\'1CLife is full of the unexpected,\u8221\'20\'1D says Minher, who was discovered through an online casting in Angola. \u8220\'20\'1CI\u8217\'20\'19m excited for every project and think even the smallest job is big.\u8221\'20\'1D\par \par \uc2 Represented by {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.thesocietymanagement.com/landing.aspx"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2  The Society Management }}}\uc2  .\par \par \uc2 _____\par \par \uc2 Margherita Tondelli\par \par \uc2 19, Italy\par \par \uc2 Tondelli\u8217\'20\'19s inaugural catwalk turn came at Chanel\u8217\'20\'19s haute couture show last month and \u8220\'20\'1Cwhen the show finished, I wanted to do it again \u8212\'20\'14 immediately,\u8221\'20\'1D she says, laughing. Coming from a small town in northern Italy that is immersed in nature, Tondelli also likes spending time in Paris. \u8220\'20\'1CI\u8217\'20\'19m passionate about art, so when I\u8217\'20\'19m in a big city, I feel super lucky to be surrounded by art and architecture masterpieces,\u8221\'20\'1D she says. \u8220\'20\'1CI also love indie music and old music.\u8221\'20\'1D She adds: \u8220\'20\'1CI don\u8217\'20\'19t even know most of the latest hits.\u8221\'20\'1D\par \par \uc2 Represented by {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.womenmanagement.com/"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2  Women Management Paris }}}\uc2  .\par \par \uc2 _____\par \par \uc2 Fernanda Oliveira\par \par \uc2 19, Brazil\par \par \uc2 Based in New York and Paris, the Brazilian-born Oliveira (who grew up in Switzerland) has gained recognition from walking the S\u227\'00\'E3o Paulo runways last fall \u8212\'20\'14 and she now plans to hit the four fashion capitals. She likes to spend her time backstage \u8220\'20\'1Cmaking everyone laugh,\u8221\'20\'1D she says. \u8220\'20\'1CI\u8217\'20\'19m not on another planet with headphones in, so I always talk and get to know people.\u8221\'20\'1D She also has an eye for styling.\par \par \uc2 