ebsite {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2016/11/10/visits-from-five-times-the-usual-number-of-americans-crashed-canadian-immigration-site.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 crashed}}}\uc2  in the hours after America\u8217\'20\'19s presidential election, thanks to a fivefold spike in the number of visitors. But the belief that Canada is a liberal utopia holds only if you have no concept of Canadian history and little knowledge of current events, and only if you walk through its cities and towns without speaking to anyone who isn\u8217\'20\'19t white, middle class or male.\par \par \uc2 On Jan. 29, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/quebec-city-mosque-gun-shots-1.3957686"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 six people were killed}}}\uc2  in a Quebec City mosque by a gunman. The suspect\u8217\'20\'19s social media use suggests support for white supremacist ideas and the Trump movement. That event, though jarring and terrifying, was neither new nor unpredictable, especially for Canada\u8217\'20\'19s Muslim citizens. The idea that Canada is a safe space is a lie \u8212\'20\'14 and an easy one to catch for anyone who has actually lived here as part of a minority group and watched how the country chooses to forget about you.\par \par \uc2 At least Mr. Trump\u8217\'20\'19s presidency will rip that falsehood open. Canada has two Trump-like candidates running for the federal Conservative leadership on platforms very similar to those that have nudged the United States and parts of Europe into the embrace of white nationalism.\par \par \uc2 After the American election, a member of Parliament named Kellie Leitch sent out an email blast calling Mr. Trump\u8217\'20\'19s win \u8220\'20\'1Can exciting message and one that we need delivered in Canada as well.\u8221\'20\'1D Before this, she attempted to establish a tip line for \u8220\'20\'1C{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/kellie-leitch-rcmp-tip-line-1.3547430"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 barbaric cultural practices}}}\uc2 ,\u8221\'20\'1D a blatant attempt to curry favor with racists and Islamophobes under the guise of protecting women and children. Ads for Ms. Leitch run on our version of Breitbart, the adorably named The Rebel, a site that traffics in hate speech. Earlier this week, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.therebel.media/what_they_won_t_tell_us_about_the_quebec_mosque_attack"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 The Rebel }}}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.therebel.media/what_they_won_t_tell_us_about_the_quebec_mosque_attack"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 wondered}}}\uc2  if the Quebec City shooter was actually a Muslim extremist rather than a white nationalist.\par \par \uc2 Meanwhile, Kevin O\u8217\'20\'19Leary, a fame-hungry \u8220\'20\'1CShark Tank\u8221\'20\'1D judge who has been living in Boston and refers to himself as \u8220\'20\'1CMr. Wonderful,\u8221\'20\'1D is the latest to announce he\u8217\'20\'19s running for the Conservative leadership. He has also argued that the 85 wealthiest people in the world having as much money as the 3.5 billion poorest is a {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://business.time.com/2014/01/22/kevin-oleary-says-3-5-billion-living-in-poverty-is-fantastic/"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 good}}}\uc2  thing.\par \par \uc2 \u8220\'20\'1CIt inspires everybody to get some motivation,\u8221\'20\'1D he said. \u8220\'20\'1COf course I applaud it.\u8221\'20\'1D\par \par \uc2 Finally, a reality show narcissist with too much money and zero government experience of our very own!\par \par \uc2 And then there\u8217\'20\'19s Mr. Trudeau himself, a colossal disappointment for liberals and conservatives alike, despite his Superman-style coiffure. He has made no attempt to publicly condemn Mr. Trump\u8217\'20\'19s race-baiting and politics of fear, presumably because he\u8217\'20\'19d worry that calling your largest trade partner a racist would hurt the aforementioned trade. In November, our eco-friendly prime minister 