\par\par \uc2 Business Day\par {\*\bkmkstart toc85}{\*\bkmkend toc85}\b \uc2 I.M.F. to Talk of Greek Bailout, and Trump Will Meet Japan\u8217\'20\'19s Leader on Trade\b0\par\par\uc2 By THE NEW YORK TIMES \par \uc2 902 \uc2 words\par \uc2 5 February 2017\par 20:00\par \uc2 NYTimes.com Feed\par \uc2 NYTFEED\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2017. The New York Times Company. All Rights Reserved. \par \par \uc2 Here\u8217\'20\'19s a look at what\u8217\'20\'19s coming up this week.\par \par \uc2 ECONOMY\par \par \uc2 Fund faces a deadline for a deal with Greece\u8217\'20\'19s creditors.\par \par \uc2 The {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.imf.org/external/index.htm"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 International Monetary Fund}}}\uc2  will hold a crucial board meeting on Monday to discuss whether it will participate in Greece\u8217\'20\'19s current bailout program, the country\u8217\'20\'19s third in seven years. The {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/organizations/i/international_monetary_fund/index.html?inline=nyt-org"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 I.M.F.}}}\uc2  has been {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/25/business/international/greece-debt-relief-imf-eurozone-bailout.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 squaring off with Greece\u8217\'20\'19s European creditors}}}\uc2  over debt calculations and austerity conditions that Greece must meet to receive badly needed loan payments. If both sides don\u8217\'20\'19t reach an agreement by Feb. 20, when European finance ministers are to meet in Brussels to review the program, the bailout could be thrown off course, pushing Greece into another potentially disastrous situation. Liz Alderman\par \par \uc2 A bank leader will discuss Trump\u8217\'20\'19s effect on the eurozone.\par \par {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/d/mario_draghi/index.html?inline=nyt-per"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 Mario Draghi}}}\uc2 , the president of the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/organizations/e/european_central_bank/index.html?inline=nyt-org"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 European Central Bank}}}\uc2 , will {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.ecb.europa.eu/home/html/index.en.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 speak to members of the European Parliament}}}\uc2  in Brussels on Monday and will probably face questions about what President Trump means for monetary policy and political unity in the eurozone. So far, Mr. Draghi has avoided commenting on Mr. Trump, but he may become more outspoken after Mr. Trump\u8217\'20\'19s tumultuous first days in office. Mr. Draghi may also face questions about whether {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.tradingeconomics.com/euro-area/inflation-cpi"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 rising inflation in the eurozone}}}\uc2  will prompt the central bank to begin withdrawing its economic stimulus measures. \uc2 Jack Ewing\par \par \uc2 December trade balance estimates are coming.\par \par \uc2 On Tuesday at 8:30 a.m., the Commerce Department will release its estimate of the trade balance for December. Economists expect to see a net deficit of $45 billion, slightly narrower than the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.tradingeconomics.com/united-states/balance-of-trade"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 $45.2 billion gap in November}}}\uc2 . The {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.economist.com/news/leaders/21711041-rise-greenback-looks-something-welcome-ignore-central-role"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 strengthening of the dollar}}}\uc2  in recent months could eventually hurt exports by making them more costly overseas, while bolstering imports as they become cheaper for American buyers. While economists don\u8217\'20\'19t expect much change in the trade balance from the preceding month, they will be watching closely for any sign of the dollar\u8217\'20\'19s impact. Nelson D. Schwartz\par \par \uc2 BANKING INDUSTRY\par \par \uc2 Several European lenders will report their 2016 results.\par \par \uc2 Investors will again have their eyes on European banks this week as several of the region\u8217\'20\'19s largest lenders report their results for 2016. {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://invest.bnpparibas.com/en"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 BNP Paribas}}}\uc2  and {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.societegenerale.com/en/investors"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 Soci\u233\'00\'E9t\u233\'00\'E9 G\u233\'00\'E9n\u233\'00\'E9rale}}}\uc2  of France and {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.unicreditgroup.eu/en/investors/financial-calendar.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 Unicredit}}}\uc2  of Italy are among the banks expected to update investors on their fourth-quarter and full-year results. \uc2 Unicredit{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.reuters.com/article/us-unicredit-capitalincrease-idUSKBN15E0MU?il=0"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 has already warned}}}\uc2  that it would post a loss of 11.8 billion euros, or about $12.7 billion, for 2016, with the bank taking \u8364\'20\'AC12.2 billion in charges in the fourth quarter as it seeks to clean up its balance sheet. Chad Bray\par \par \uc2 ECONOMY\par \par \uc2 Mexican banking leaders will meet as the peso weakens.\par \par \uc2 Mexico\u8217\'20\'19s central bank\uc2  board will meet on Thursday amid expectations that it will announce a rate increase to address rising inflation. A weakening peso and the government\u8217\'20\'19s decision to deregulate gasoline prices at the beginning of the year led to the sharpest spike in inflation in almost two decades. Now the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/08/world/americas/unrest-mexico-pena-nieto-gas-prices-trump.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 fuel shock}}}\uc2  is beginning to spread as prices of basic goods are rising and analysts forecast that inflation could surpass 5 percent. The peso has recovered some ground after hitting a {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/05/world/americas/mexico-pena-nieto-trump-turmoil-gasoline.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 historic low}}}\uc2  two weeks ago in the face of uncertainty about relations with the United States, which buys almost 80 percent of Mexican exports. That uncertainty puts more strain on the Mexican economy, as companies may delay investment plans while waiting to see what comes of {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.nytimes.com/2017/02/01/world/americas/mexico-nafta-renegotiation-trump-wall.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 talks to renegotiate}}}\uc2  the \uc2 North American Free Trade Agreement\uc2 . Elisabeth Malkin\par \par \uc2 TECHNOLOGY\par \par \uc2 Twitter\uc2  will announce its 2016 earnings.\par \par \uc2 Twitter\uc2  will report its {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://files.shareholder.com/downloads/AMDA-2F526X/3812126078x0x923197/12B828A1-605D-4CBF-B8B8-E75266ADD294/TWTR_Q416_Earnings_Date_Announcement.pdf"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 financial results}}}\uc2  for the fourth quarter of 2016 and the full year on Thursday. Wall Street expects the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/28/technology/twitter-job-cuts-q3-earnings.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 beleaguered social media company}}}\uc2  to announce revenue of $736 million for the fourth quarter. As always, analysts will closely watch the company\u8217\'20\'19s user growth figures, a point of difficulty for \uc2 Twitter\uc2  since its initial public offering in 2013. Mike Isaac\par \par \uc2 ECONOMY\par \par \uc2 Trump and Japan\u8217\'20\'19s prime minister are poised to meet.\par \par \uc2 President Trump is scheduled to meet Prime Minister {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/a/shinzo_abe/index.html?inline=nyt-per"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 Shinzo Abe}}}\uc2  of Japan on Friday, with trade and currency issues high on the agenda. Mr. Abe\u8217\'20\'19s goal is to {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2017/01/31/world/asia/ap-as-japan-us-currency.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 defuse accusations by Mr. Trump}}}\uc2  that Japan benefits unfairly from trade with the United States, partly by keeping the yen artificially cheap. He may offer to channel Japanese investment into American industries in hopes of forestalling {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/subjects/p/protectionism_trade/index.html?inline=nyt-classifier"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 protectionism}}}\uc2 . Much is at stake: The United States is Japan\u8217\'20\'19s most important overseas market, and the meeting could set the course for future bilateral trade negotiations. That is especially crucial, now that Mr. Trump has said Washington will {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/25/business/trump-tpp-japan-trade.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 no longer }}}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/25/business/trump-tpp-japan-trade.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 participate}}}\uc2  in the Trans-Pacific Partnership trade deal, negotiated by the Obama administration. Jonathan Soble\par \par \uc2 Consumer sentiment estimates are on the way.\par \par \uc2 On Friday at 10 a.m., the \b \highlight22\uc2 University\b0 \highlight\uc2  of Michigan\uc2  will release its initial estimate of consumer sentiment for February. The \b \highlight22\uc2 University\b0 \highlight\uc2  of Michigan\uc2 \u8217\'20\'19s index hit a 13-year high last month, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://ns.umich.edu/new/releases/24495-consumer-optimism-surges-in-january-amid-partisanship"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 98.5}}}\uc2 , and economists expect a slight decrease to 97.7. That is still a healthy reading, as income gains, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.nytimes.com/2017/02/03/business/economy/unemployment-jobs-report-hiring.html"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 steady hiring}}}\uc2  and a {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://markets.on.nytimes.com/research/markets/overview/overview.asp"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 surging stock market}}}\uc2  have improved consumers\u8217\'20\'19 outlook. Nelson D. Schwartz\par \par \uc2 Mario Draghi is the president of the European Central Bank. | Yves Herman/Reuters \par \par \uc2 Document NYTFEED020170206ed26001b9\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw284\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4260\pichgoal600
